### Key Point

```text
height - 1 = 4
diameter   = 6
```

The longest path lies completely inside the right subtree, so height cannot find it.

Therefore:

```text
Return value -> Height of subtree

ans -> Maximum diameter found anywhere in the tree
```

That's why we update:

```cpp
ans = max(ans, leftHeight + rightHeight);
```

at every node.


